{"tid":2254793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自家網站變國際文宣平台 籲同路人錄音  祖瑟夫抗爭詩撐港「自由戰士 聲音會被聽見」","createTime":"2020-10-23T05:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T05:46:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ead00e344acbae774d01cdf3a1b79c9b626521","tid":2254793,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201023/LOYBJWS255EQPP2ZVD2XKCUJSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201023%2FLOYBJWS255EQPP2ZVD2XKCUJSE%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b20db8d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201023%2FLOYBJWS255EQPP2ZVD2XKCUJSE%2F&h=3af1cc79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201023/LOYBJWS255EQPP2ZVD2XKCUJSE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n自家網站變國際文宣平台 籲同路人錄音 <br />\n祖瑟夫抗爭詩撐港「自由戰士 聲音會被聽見」<br />\n<br />\n荷李活男星祖瑟夫哥頓利域（Joseph Gordon-Levitt）早前兩度於fb向網民徵求香港靚相，計劃在自家創立的網上平台hitRECord，炮製一個關於香港的作品，有不少網民貼上反送中遊行和示威的照片，令網站頓變一個國際文宣平台。昨日祖瑟夫更於fb呼籲香港人為英文詩《香港永不眠》錄音，詩中用字及語句均明撐香港的逆權運動。詩句中讚頌港人是「自由戰士」，而且「聲音會被聽見」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【童星拍劇】憑《心跳500天》蜚聲國際<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jmG6EC1xY-HnygazZpDJJ78MGHA=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z65DVUYESFFOVOAMPIMMGOIW5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjmG6EC1xY-HnygazZpDJJ78MGHA%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ65DVUYESFFOVOAMPIMMGOIW5E.jpg&h=968f028e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■祖瑟夫發佈名為《Hong Kong Never Sleeps》的英文詩，有不少對逆權之戰的描寫，形容港人為「自由戰士」，且「聲音會被聽見」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n過去一年，香港經歷了抗暴之戰，引起國際關注。39歲荷李活男星祖瑟夫哥頓利域今年8月在fb向網民徵求香港靚相，計劃在他創立的網上平台hitRECord炮製一個關於香港的作品，他上個月再度在fb上載一張香港夜景照片，並再呼籲網民盡快提供照片，結果連日來網民踴躍貼上各類反送中遊行和示威照片，令網站頓變一個國際文宣平台。9月時王宗堯亦有在fb回應祖瑟夫，感謝他與香港同行，又貼上港人高舉美國國旗的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P_fRnmTVGxcjUhIjL8gM4mvMr-o=/1860x864/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C2XSWALBA5HCRIXZSTIPOIEV2Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP_fRnmTVGxcjUhIjL8gM4mvMr-o%3D%2F1860x864%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC2XSWALBA5HCRIXZSTIPOIEV2Q.gif&h=b32f8302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Brgb4nG6n9Ln6FLQ3p7W-Tse6z8=/1417x477/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JVWI6R4EHVEH7KCJ2WNER35XUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBrgb4nG6n9Ln6FLQ3p7W-Tse6z8%3D%2F1417x477%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJVWI6R4EHVEH7KCJ2WNER35XUQ.gif&h=d4094d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■祖瑟夫於自家網上平台hitRECord製作關於香港的作品，不少fans近日趁機上載逆權運動照片，令網站變成國際文宣平台。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港，淚如雨下」<br />\n<br />\n及至昨日，祖瑟夫再於fb呼籲香港人，為一首擺明撐香港逆權運動的詩錄音，他於fb表示：「有香港人有興趣錄音嗎？我在找幾個人讀出以下幾句，你只需要一個電話！」並附上一張有IFC及天星小輪的維港照片。該篇詩名為《香港永不眠》（Hong Kong Never Sleeps），詩句中不乏港人在抗爭中的描述，包括：「香港，自有天地，在這裏我們譜寫自己的歷史」、「香港，淚如雨下，人們因上街聚在一起」、「自由的戰士，有着痛苦的臉，聲音都會被聽見」等。是次邀請是為了用在新計劃Passport Poems系列，截至昨日黃昏8小時內已超過400人上載聲帶聲演該詩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lWYDKR2QpSM3G39eVOV2H_0-0U4=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5XU3WSHY55D3REH7L67GR73I3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlWYDKR2QpSM3G39eVOV2H_0-0U4%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5XU3WSHY55D3REH7L67GR73I3Q.jpg&h=3e13d46f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■莎朗史東上月受訪主動問起香港近況，讚港人勇敢之餘又向港人做出致敬手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XiWoSkapN5qYPA1yGgZaKh0CEjg=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P3UIGZI4ZNCGPDX7BNEIAD3S5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXiWoSkapN5qYPA1yGgZaKh0CEjg%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP3UIGZI4ZNCGPDX7BNEIAD3S5E.jpg&h=e4b5944a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《移動迷宮》男星Will（小圖）月前於社交網轉載香港示威報道，留言力撐港人爭取民主 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhitRECord成共創平台<br />\n<br />\n曾主演《潛行凶間》（Inception）及《蝙蝠俠：夜神起義》（The Dark Knight Rises）等多部電影的祖瑟夫，與哥哥Dan於2004年成立了hitRECord網站，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其實自去年逆權運動以來，已有不少荷李活藝人相繼為港人發聲。62歲的莎朗史東（Sharon Stone）上月接受《蘋果》記者視像訪問，主動問起香港近況，不但指心繫香港，大讚港人勇敢，並含淚向港人做出致敬手勢。今年8.31太子站恐襲事件一周年，電影《移動迷宮》（The Maze Runner）27歲英國男星Will Poulter於社交網轉載當日示威報道，並留言力撐港人爭取民主自由，又在Ig的限時動態張貼五一手勢emoji。至於18歲新紮美國樂壇天后Billie Eilish今年6月於Ig中，亦。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Om1-wV6BNRO_ij0PTuSKoxt0pxw=/850x1079/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MGPQ24S5QBCX3HON43DGNV5OCA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOm1-wV6BNRO_ij0PTuSKoxt0pxw%3D%2F850x1079%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMGPQ24S5QBCX3HON43DGNV5OCA.gif&h=5086409b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ba17e3f37d0af7f825bea523ddcf65ebe691a46","tid":2254793,"uid":262274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"反觀香港班僞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}